{"tid":2487702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登將美軍撤離阿富汗期限推遲至9月11日","createTime":"2021-04-13T17:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T18:16:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"931cd5e7d1836d2e5963c2836899d3e63edfae2e","tid":2487702,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:50:03.000Z","msg":"美國將無法實現前特朗普政府提出，下月1日前從阿富汗撤軍的計劃，多名消息人士指，總統拜登已決定將撤軍期限推遲至今年9月11日，預計到訪布魯塞爾的國務卿布林肯與國防部長奧斯汀，會向北約成員國簡報有關決定，拜登亦可能公開宣布。 <br />\n<br />\n特朗普政府曾與塔利班簽署協議，將5月1日定為美軍撤出阿富汗的期限，但拜登早已暗示會將撤軍日子延後。塔利班肯上月曾警告，如果美國不在下月前撤走，將恢復針對外國部隊的敵對行動。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2387075\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2387075&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11Fm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=c9585063\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2387075</a>"},{"pid":"a791ceb73a85287d8484a669fc346771a1893cff","tid":2487702,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:51:14.000Z","msg":"黑馬都講過類似嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68796244f9ae7cd5cda52680acf5988c528b84b4","tid":2487702,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:59:02.000Z","msg":"好揀唔揀，係都要揀911 呢個對美國人嚟講一個不祥嘅數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1f0c3579949ac0c0c7b7fe2768c7a0773fd42f","tid":2487702,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T18:00:41.000Z","msg":"佢都係將軍咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89f90cf764dd6a3cc7025ed606b00759b36b292","tid":2487702,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T18:02:18.000Z","msg":"唔留點開更多軍火contract<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />deep state搵真銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce44ad0d